        * protocols/ace/INet/URLBase.cpp (ACE): Changed

          if (pos > 0 && url_string[pos+1] == '/' && url_string[pos+1] == '/')

          to

          if (pos > 0 && url_string[pos+1] == '/' && url_string[pos+2] == '/')

